The paper discusses the design of a neuromemristive system for unsupervised learning, which falls under the category of neural networks and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The use of memristors in the system also suggests that it could fall under cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), which deals with new and innovative technologies in computer science. The paper also discusses the performance of the system, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the system is designed for clustering, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
